    stable 1.2.2
  category audio/player
 attribute console
    source http://www.johnath.com/beep/beep-$VERSION.tar.gz
  homepage http://www.johnath.com/beep
      desc 'beep the pc speaker in any number of ways
Different sounds can indicate different events.
While it can be run quite happily on the commandline,
it is intended place of residence is within shell/perl scripts,
notifying the user when something interesting occurs.
Of course, it has no notion of what is interesting,
but it is real good at the notifying part.'

build(){
make &&
prepare_install &&
make    install
}
